    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Lamps for lighting that use LEDs, organic light-emitting diodes (OLEDs), or light-emitting polymers consisting of semiconductors that convert electricity into light. Solid-state lighting is used in a variety of lighting applications because it is energy-efficient, environmentally friendly, and has longer life. They are also considered durable, intrinsically safe, and ideal for smaller, flexible light fixtures.</Note_Text>
